 1. What is this application?

Name: AI Multi-Agent Reliability Microservice Gateway
It is a backend microservice + dashboard that sits between users and multiple AI models (like OpenAI, Gemini, etc.).
Instead of your app directly calling one AI model, it calls this gateway, and the gateway:

The AI Multi-Agent Reliability Microservice Gateway is a backend microservice + admin dashboard that sits between users and multiple AI models (OpenAI, Gemini, Claude, etc.).
Instead of your app calling a single AI model directly, it calls this gateway, which:

Runs the request through multiple AI agents
â†’ Generator â†’ Safety â†’ Quality
Selects the best provider/model
Applies retries, fallbacks, timeouts, and circuit breakers
Performs safety & quality validation
Uses caching to reduce cost and improve speed
Logs every request for metrics, monitoring, and debugging

In simple words:
It is a smart control center that guarantees safe, reliable, high-quality AI responses.

